# ChangeLog for clip-layout/baselayout-sdk

*baselayout-sdk-1.3.1-r3 (15 Sep 2017)

  15 Sep 2017; Nicolas Godinho <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-sdk-1.3.1-r3.ebuild, -baselayout-sdk-1.3.1-r2.ebuild:
  Set SDK GCC version to the same as the RM GCC version (since dev-libs/icu
  needs at least GCC 4.9 and is needed within the SDK for CMake and Subversion).

*baselayout-sdk-1.3.1-r2 (13 Sep 2017)

  13 Sep 2017; Alain Ozanne <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-sdk-1.3.1-r2.ebuild, -baselayout-sdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Update to have gcc 4.9.3 as a dependency used for rm jails compilations.

*baselayout-sdk-1.3.1-r1 (03 May 2016)

  03 May 2016; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-sdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild, -baselayout-sdk-1.3.1.ebuild:
  Add warning in clip-fetch for bug 3547.

*baselayout-sdk-1.3.1 (22 Mar 2016)

  22 Mar 2016; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-sdk-1.3.1.ebuild, -baselayout-sdk-1.3.0.ebuild:
  Update gcc version to 5.3.0 for amd64

*baselayout-sdk-1.3.0 (11 Feb 2016)

  11 Feb 2016; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-sdk-1.3.0.ebuild, -baselayout-sdk-1.2.17.ebuild:
  Update portage overlays with extra dirs.
  Install clip-fetch to deal with auto symlink creation and
  new portage profiles.

*baselayout-sdk-1.2.17 (09 Feb 2016)

  09 Feb 2016; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-sdk-1.2.17.ebuild, -baselayout-sdk-1.2.16.ebuild:
  Fix configured GCC version on amd64.

*baselayout-sdk-1.2.16 (02 Dec 2015)

  02 Dec 2015; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-sdk-1.2.16.ebuild, -baselayout-sdk-1.2.15-r1.ebuild:
  Update gcc version to 4.9.3 on amd64.

*baselayout-sdk-1.2.15 (01 Dec 2015)

  01 Dec 2015; Alain Ozanne <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
