*baselayout-sdk-1.2.10-r2 (08 Oct 2013)

  08 Oct 2013; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-sdk-1.2.10-r2.ebuild, -baselayout-sdk-1.2.10-r1.ebuild:
  Handle a clip-sdk-bootstrap USE flag. Don't use gcc-config when it's set, so
  don't bring a huge dependency list, useful for early bootstrap stages.

*baselayout-sdk-1.2.10-r1 (10 Sep 2013)

